rows.label: qst201914_msg0001
rows.name:
The black-feathered fool
named Suisui should be
somewhere in this city...

rows.label: qst201914_msg0004
rows.name:
I was prepared, mo, but to think
you would actually come this far...
what a persistent woman, mo...

rows.label: qst201914_msg0005
rows.name:
Fufufu... The day of
reckoning has come...

rows.label: qst201914_msg0006
rows.name: Now! Return all of our money!

rows.label: qst201914_msg0007
rows.name:
Hmph! As if I would just return
it because you say so, mo!

rows.label: qst201914_msg0008
rows.name:
If you're so upset, try
and catch Suisui, mo!

rows.label: qst201914_msg0009
rows.name:
Though I doubt you can get through
the best mercenaries in Superbia,
hired with most of your money, mo.

rows.label: qst201914_msg0010
rows.name: You...! You wasted our money on them?!

rows.label: qst201914_msg0011
rows.name:
Let us defeat them quickly
and chase after that
black-feathered fool at once!
